The '''1903 [[VMI Keydets]] football team''' represented the [[Virginia Military Institute]] in their thirteenth ever season of organized football. The Keydets finished a short year at 2-1 lead by 1st-year head coach [[William Roper (American football)|William Roper]].<ref name="VMI">http://www.vmikeydets.com/pdf8/708636.pdf</ref>
